# 🚀 Featured Projects

### 🤖 Enterprise HR Assistant
> AI-powered HR assistant using RAG, LLMs and semantic search over company documents.

**Tech:** Flask • LangChain • Pinecone • ChromaDB • MongoDB • Supabase

---

### 🧠 Multi-RAG Framework

A modular retrieval system implementing

- Traditional RAG
- Hybrid RAG
- Graph RAG
- Corrective RAG
- Cache RAG
- Agentic RAG

---

### 📈 Stock Market Prediction

Machine learning models for predicting S&P 500 excess returns while satisfying volatility constraints.

**Result:** Top 300 globally in Kaggle competition.

---

### 🌧 RechargeTwin

AI-powered Digital Twin for Rainwater Recharge Pit Health Monitoring using IoT, Computer Vision and Predictive Analytics.

